---
// Footer.astro
---

<footer
  class="bg-gradient-to-b from-stone-100 to-stone-200 text-stone-800 py-16 px-6"
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Sección principal del footer -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-12">
      <!-- Logo y descripción -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-1">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border-2 border-orange-300 flex items-center justify-center mr-4"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-6 h-6 text-stone-700"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zM21 5H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a4 4 0 004 4h10V5z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900">BA</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-600 font-light">ATELIER</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Donde cada prenda es una obra de arte creada con pasión y atención al
          detalle. Experiencia exclusiva en alta costura.
        </p>
        <!-- Redes sociales -->
        <div class="flex space-x-4">
          <a
            href="#"
            class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-stone-300 hover:bg-orange-300 transition-colors duration-300 flex items-center justify-center"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 text-stone-700"
              fill="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
